The paper deals with physical layer security in a multi-antenna downlink network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The focus is on the security aspect, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions MIMO (cs.MM) and system parameters (cs.SY) in the context of mode selection.
